Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must run forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,If you are still burning with furious rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Mada ikari ni moeru toshi ga aru nara...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Mr. Ryu, standby okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, standby for docking.\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in, Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam B Parts released!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Change! Docking, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Days spent training with comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...to perfect the mid-air docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After deserting the White Base,\Nwill the wayward Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...ever experience those days again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For an Amuro wandering the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...feelings similar to regret\Nwere beginning to emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral's Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have some water to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have any to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a town close by. Buy some there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a meal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree with everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- About Amuro?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we considering Amuro\Nseparately from the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... We'll make a decision about Amuro\Nafter we get the Gundam back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's forget it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all depend on\Nhow Amuro feels at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Time to get some food!\N- I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister. We're taking a break.\NThere're 13 of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hamon, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sagred and Mile. You'll keep watch.\NI'll make sure you're relieved soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lieutenant Ramba Ral.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some water, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...you must be amazed\Nthat there's a desert this big on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a marvel of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Much more interesting than star-gazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, at ease! Take a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have anything you want.\NIt's the last meal before our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the mission...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sodon is considered neutral territory,\Nso no combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it elsewhere. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have much here...\NWe'll have 14 of whatever you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one too many, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One for the boy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're interested in a boy like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, he's gotta eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? In a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't know how to say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your generosity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I can't accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you\Nto give me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid's got you there, Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just took a liking to you, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a good enough reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid. It's quite something\Nto be liked by Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NIt's bad karma to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I were in your shoes, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be thankful you were born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a beggar either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, kid.\NYou don't mince words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just from Hamon, it's from me too.\NYou can accept the meal then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant!\NWe found a suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- A spy?\N- Yes! A woman behaving strangely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's wearing a Federation uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure? It looks a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Hamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she's this boy's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've got some guts.\NNow, I'm really impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we should meet in battle,\Nit will be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, young Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Ramba Ral.\NAnd Ms. Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro!\N- Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go follow them, Zeygan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The only Federation forces around here\Nshould be the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think everyone will continue\Nto worry about you... you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who got caught by the Zeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what were YOU doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't want to hold hands with me\Nbecause that lady was watching, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're wrong.\N- Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just getting further and further\Naway from me, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Aren't you going to the White Base?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Better get back soon,\Nor you'll get sunstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll regret this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can manage on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's come in?\N- A coded message from Zeygan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,'The wind will blow soon.'\NSeems he found the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Begin preparations for the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw a Gouf? The enemy mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Stowed on two large trailers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw him in Sodon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Amuro told the Zeons\Nabout the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, enough with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy forces are stalking us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We should stop maintenance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and put the White Base\Non interception status.\N- I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't just go off without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working well.\NStetch! How's your mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sir! It's running well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right. You guys advance 5 kilometers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't use the radio for now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are those people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the enemy we're fighting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just took a liking to you, that's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's quite something{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they found the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have followed Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If that Gouf mobile suit shows up...\Nthe Guncannon and Guntank are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... It's so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu, get us away from White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy has two mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get any closer to White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stetch! I'll leap out...\Nand then you destroy the tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lieutenant Ral!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! A caterpillar track was hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it, Lieutenant! I got the tank!\NNow I'll finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been paying attention? Stetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to take out the Trojan Horse,\Nor there's no point to our battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, sir...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! I'm doing a forced ejection\Nof the Guntank's upper unit! All right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forced ejection?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hayato! What about you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu, I've got plenty of ammo left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just act as a turret!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't waste strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu, please take the Core Fighter\Nand find Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I understand.\NYou could be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching core block!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, cover Hayato and the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are the Gouf and Zaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! You should get out of there\Nbefore you're killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move, but I still have ammo!\NI'm staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. How very noble of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the enemy up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use the beam rifle now,\Nwhen I fight the Gouf, I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do you read?! I'll keep it occupied!\NYou head over to the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu came to look for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ascend. We're escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on! Even the Trojan Horse can't take\Na direct missile from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One Zaku approaching the stern!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about our rear missiles?\N- There's no one there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's right behind us?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Full speed ahead! Hang on tight, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Careless fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Kai! Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hit the Gouf from outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't destroy it, the White Base will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! I'll shake off the Gouf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mirai, can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to fly upside-down.\NPlease fasten your seatbelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about you?\N- Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai is amazing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one they call the Gundam!\NWhere was it hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That Amuro! Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Gouf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some precise firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, it's easy for the computer to predict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not even dodging them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've only got one shot left anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This pilot's got some guts!\NA tough opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What amazing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Gundam!\NBut my control systems are still intact!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...! That kid from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name's Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You let us go just so you could\Nfind the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Times certainly have changed,\Nwith kids like you fighting as pilots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's he...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive! But remember, kid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own strength didn't win the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the performance of your mobile suit!\NDon't forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a sore loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.\NI'll meet up with Hamon later tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Top priority is to recover Hayato's Guntank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We've taken too much damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Open a comm circuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to help with the recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever your reasons were,\Nyou're guilty of damaging our teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too one-sided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't leave the White Base on a whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to hear my side of it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When Ramba Ral attacks,\NI'll have to pilot the Gundam anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I went looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... without me, you can't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so conceited.\NWe just wanted the Gundam back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You should think long and hard about that!\NEh, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do repairs all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems even that Gallop of theirs\Ngot damaged... but they'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd understand if you listened to me!\NLet me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to lock me up in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! Or even Ms. Mirai!\NMs. Sayla! Please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me... I have things to say too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can hear me on the TV monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me! Ms. Sayla! Ms. Sayla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundam...\Nbetter than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use it better than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be so conceited!t win the battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You won because of Gundam's performance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've got guts.likes you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my treat, Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to beat that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy finally boards the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The young crew resists the intruders\Nin the midst of terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As guns blaze,\Nthe Gundam destroys the Gallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the cost of this victory is high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...resulting in significant losses for\NAmuro and the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NHand-to-Hand Combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand-to-Hand Combat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:58.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:09.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:14.05,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:18.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:24.06,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:28.65,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:38.95,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
